    </\f[B]tr\f[R]>
  </\f[B]tbody\f[R]>
</\f[B]table\f[R]>
<\f[B]button\f[R] id=\(dqadd\(dq>Add a row</\f[B]button\f[R]>
<\f[B]button\f[R] id=\(dqremove\(dq>Remove last row</\f[B]button\f[R]>
<\f[B]div\f[R]>This table\(aqs body has <\f[B]output\f[R]>1</\f[B]output\f[R]> row(s).</\f[B]div\f[R]>
